data.description: Freshly updated brick, split level home in La Grange Park! This move-in ready home has just been updated with new fixtures, paint, and fresh carpet. It's simply not possible to find a home this large and move-in ready elsewhere in La Grange Park. The home sits on 1/3 acre corner lot on a street lined with mature trees, offers nearly 2,500 square feet, and features a number of recent improvements, including newer garage siding, fixtures, refrigerator, kitchen flooring, furnace (all 2021) and dishwasher (2023). Highlights include a spacious, split-level layout, hardwood flooring, crown molding, an amazing sunroom, four bedrooms plus a large office (which could be used as a fifth bedroom), three full bathrooms, ample yard space, and a three car garage. Located in the highly rated Park, Forest, & Lyons Township school districts, which Niche has rated A, A, and A+, respectively, just moments from downtown La Grange & downtown Brookfield.
